# Output format

Return a JSON object matching this exact schema:

{
  "vertical_score": <0.0 to 1.0>,
  "vertical_reasoning": "<one or two sentences>",
  "conflicts": [
    {
      "peer_okr_id": "<the id from above, or null for vertical-only>",
      "peer_title": "<title of the conflicting OKR>",
      "conflict_type": "<resource | metric | scope | timing>",
      "description": "<one sentence describing the conflict>",
      "severity": "<info | warning | blocking>"
    }
  ],
  "verdict": "<aligned | needs_review | blocked>",
  "suggestions": ["<concrete suggestion>", ...]
}

Output ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no commentary, no markdown fences.
